name: Coronavirus Leakage Laboratory
description:
The Coronavirus has dominated the W.H. Laboratory in a country somewhere named "Wall Country".

Wall Country government president sent out the Virus Slayer, to clean up all variants of the giant virus.

When the virus evolves will be more lethality and more faster-moving

The resources leftover in the laboratory is the only way to protect or fight back the giant virus.

But no one survives complete their mission.

The Great Communist Party is our homes and into our hearts.

  • BTW, please don't input some weird number or characters that should not be allowed in the country,  this will trigger the Fragile Heart.
  • Please make sure to maintain your own personal hygiene.
